# Default owner for the whole repo. Replace @8hats/maintainers with the
# actual maintainer team or individual handles, then enable branch
# protection on `main` requiring "Require review from Code Owners".
* @8hats/maintainers

# Workflow files have GITHUB_TOKEN with `contents: write` — they can
# create releases and tag the repo. Anything touching .github/ should
# require a maintainer review.
/.github/                @8hats/maintainers
/.github/workflows/      @8hats/maintainers
/.github/dependabot.yml  @8hats/maintainers
/CODEOWNERS              @8hats/maintainers
/.claude-plugin/         @8hats/maintainers
/package.json            @8hats/maintainers
